{"tid":2427505,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無中文系可以解釋個「氈」字","createTime":"2021-02-28T23:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T07:00:36.000Z","uid":232575,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"341a2e1f47bf0262ef1159ab79810934e45e04ce","tid":2427505,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVwedmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVwedmc.png&h=2d1ae460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《說文》：「氈，撚毛也。從毛亶聲。」<br />\n真係唔識解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%B0%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%25E6%25B0%2588&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3cZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=dc8f122a\" target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%B0%88</a>"},{"pid":"8701f1bda4297006780af86d1334a0a673b95d0d","tid":2427505,"uid":392181,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:02:05.000Z","msg":"解釋：<br />\n<br />\n1. 用手指揉搓。<br />\n【例】撚紙<br />\n2. 用手指捏取、夾取。<br />\n【例】撚花、撚香<br />\n3. 一種彈奏琵琶的手法。即揉弄、撥弄。<br />\n【例】輕攏慢撚抹復挑。（唐．白居易〈琵琶行〉"},{"pid":"46d2c2aa3c145cc22e7819dd9d2aac4a3f8311ec","tid":2427505,"uid":122117,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:09:20.000Z","msg":"我手頭上有本說文解字 認真答<br />\n「撚」代表輕輕拎取、提取既意思<br />\n呢個網並未完全摘錄書入面既解釋，其實後面仲有其他補充，「撚毛者、蹂毛成氈也」「撚毛也。或曰撚，執也，蹂也。蹂毛成片，故謂之氈。」<br />\n氈既意思係「取毛的人，將毛組織成為片狀，即為氈。」"},{"pid":"07d1686e0fbdf76ae47fb56ac9fd9f39194a4a31","tid":2427505,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"謝兩位賜教<br />\n另外，<br />\n「撚」可以讀nin2，其實係咪「鏈」住條頸個「鏈」既正字?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%92%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%25E6%2592%259A&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3cZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=2c04a99a\" target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%92%9A</a>"},{"pid":"24d97e54a998c253af5cd8ca0709048364bc68ec","tid":2427505,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:47:46.000Z","msg":"段注：<br />\n手部曰。<strong>撚者、蹂也。</strong>撚毛者、<strong>蹂毛成氈也。</strong>周禮掌皮曰。共其毳毛爲氈。古多假旃字。"},{"pid":"9769e0a55dc8137356f225f966b06ef4c65bbf8f","tid":2427505,"uid":122117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d1686e0fbdf76ae47fb56ac9fd9f39194a4a31","tid":2427505,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"謝兩位賜教<br />\n另外，<br />\n「撚」可以讀nin2，其實係咪「鏈」住條頸個「鏈」既正字?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%92%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%25E6%2592%259A&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3cZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=2c04a99a\" target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%92%9A</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"「鏈」係 lin<br />\n「撚」係 nin<br />\n<br />\n加返鼻音"},{"pid":"06ad8b9e54188ef57ed2d8f7cccc11eb0c00ab53","tid":2427505,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9769e0a55dc8137356f225f966b06ef4c65bbf8f","tid":2427505,"uid":122117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d1686e0fbdf76ae47fb56ac9fd9f39194a4a31","tid":2427505,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"謝兩位賜教<br />\n另外，<br />\n「撚」可以讀nin2，其實係咪「鏈」住條頸個「鏈」既正字?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E6%92%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%25E6%2592%259A&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NK